{"tid":2079200,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳門稱粵澳專家認同珠海與澳門同屬疫情低風險地區","createTime":"2020-06-25T15:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T15:31:57.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"995b06a496db8b77c385573f8ca491bc3361d79e","tid":2079200,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:31:57.000Z","msg":"澳門稱粵澳專家認同珠海與澳門同屬疫情低風險地區<br />\n2020-06-25 HKT 22:52<br />\n<br />\n澳門與珠海將會在防控新型肺炎措施上，保持一致，建立兩地共同救治的機制，資源共享；同時會加強兩地環境和重點人群的動態監測，聯合進行流行病學調查，以及參考內地政策，實行分區管理等。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534132-20200625.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534132-20200625.htm&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SswxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=51bc1e91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534132-20200625.htm&h=ab6e5453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534132-20200625.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n珠海與澳門同屬疫情低風險地區，所以大家很快將可去澳門及珠海旅遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"}]}